title: [Warrior Guild, Western Grove]
description: A small stream cuts across the clearing, but is easily crossed.  Silvery fish dance in the shallow depths of the water, darting downstream in a rhythmic flash of color.  One of the groundskeeper's children sits nearby, happily off in her own world.
A small stream cuts across the clearing, but can be easily crossed.  The distorted reflection of the moon drifts serenely off the surface of the water, disturbed only when somebody strolls past.
